1638
01:12:58.945 --> 01:13:02.045
as predicted, MUIDS wrecked havoc on native wildlife.

1639
01:13:02.045 --> 01:13:03.965
Today, we call ourselves Kiwis.

1640
01:13:04.025 --> 01:13:06.045
